{"body":"`cargo binstall` is installing `cargo-audit`/`cargo-machete` without pinning versions, which makes CI non-reproducible and can start failing unexpectedly when new upstream releases land. Consider pinning tool versions (or at least using a lockfile/explicit versions) so the CI environment is deterministic, similar to how `cargo-zigbuild` is version-pinned elsewhere in this workflow.\n```suggestion\n        run: cargo binstall --no-confirm cargo-audit@0.21.2 cargo-machete@0.7.0\n```","line":22,"path":".github/workflows/ci.yml","user":"Copilot"}
